description.fr: Les Shushus semblent regagner en force, si bien qu'ils risquent de redevenir problème. {CharacterName:474} doit agir sans attendre.
description.en: The Shushus seem to be getting stronger, and are likely going to become a problem again. {CharacterName:474} must act immediately.
description.es: Los fab'huritus parecen estar recuperando su fuerza, tanto que corren el riesgo de convertirse de nuevo en un problema. {CharacterName:474} debe actuar sin demora.
description.de: Die Shushus scheinen wieder stärker zu werden. Damit könnten sie bald wieder zum Problem werden. {CharacterName:474} muss umgehend eingreifen.
description.pt: Os Shushus parecem ter recobrado sua força e podem acabar se tornando um problema de novo. {CharacterName:474} deve agir logo.

descriptionFinished.fr: Pour endiguer l'invasion Shushu, {CharacterName:474} a envoyé {CharacterName:596} traquer les démons à travers tout le Monde des Douze. En parallèle, elle a également chargé {CharacterName:708} et {CharacterName:654} de surveiller la faille apparue sur {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}. De son côté, {CharacterName:474} espère comprendre le message de la {Summoning:1354}...
descriptionFinished.en: To stop the Shushu invasion, {CharacterName:474} has sent {CharacterName:596} to track down the demons throughout the World of Twelve. At the same time, she's also sent {CharacterName:708} and {CharacterName:654} to guard the rift that appeared on {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}. For her part, {CharacterName:474} hopes to figure out the {Summoning:1354}'s message…
descriptionFinished.es: Para contener la invasión fab'hurita, {CharacterName:474} ha enviado a {CharacterName:596} a perseguir a los demonios por todo el Mundo de los Doce. Al mismo tiempo, también ha encargado a {CharacterName:708} y {CharacterName:654} que vigilen la falla que ha aparecido en {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}. Por su parte, {CharacterName:474} espera comprender el mensaje de la {Summoning:1354}…
descriptionFinished.de: Um die Shushu-Invasion aufzuhalten, hat {CharacterName:474} {CharacterName:596} geschickt, um die Dämonen kreuz und quer durch die Welt der Zwölf zu jagen. Gleichzeitig hat sie außerdem {CharacterName:708} und {CharacterName:654} damit beauftragt, den Riss im Auge zu behalten, der sich in {WorldZone:208[Astrub]} aufgetan hat. {CharacterName:474} hofft ihrerseits, die Nachricht der {Summoning:1354} entschlüsseln zu können\_...
descriptionFinished.pt: Para conter a invasão Shushu, {CharacterName:474} enviou {CharacterName:596} para caçar esses demônios por todo o Mundo dos Doze. Além disso, também encarregou {CharacterName:708} e {CharacterName:654} de vigiar a falha que surgiu em {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}. Enquanto isso, {CharacterName:474} espera conseguir entender a mensagem da {Summoning:1354}…
